subject: Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
lead_paragraph: Kyle Larson, who will begin his first full season in the Nascar Sprint Cup Series at the Daytona 500 on Sunday, is expected to contend for rookie of the year honors.
